sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant System
    
    Note over Player, System: UC-06: Cast Ranged Spell
    Player->>System: openInventory()
    Player->>System: clickItem("Spell Book")
    Player->>System: selectAction("READ")
    System->>System: checkMana(spellCost)
    
    alt Sufficient Mana
        System->>System: deductMana(spellCost)
        System->>System: createProjectile(Hero.x, Hero.y, direction)
        System-->>Player: renderProjectilePath()
        System->>System: apply damage on hit
    else Insufficient Mana
        System-->>Player: display lack of mana message
    end